      },
      "rdfs:label": "A photocaged NbALFA variant (ALFA-Pb, Tyr42ONBY substitution) reduces affinity to Kd 3.2\u20137.9 \u00b5M in the dark and restores near-wild-type affinity (~183\u2013346 pM) after 365 nm UV irradiation, enabling light-controlled binding to the ALFA tag."
