      "cat:documented": false,
      "cat:slug": "HK022_attB",
      "dcterms:description": "Phage HK022 bacterial attachment site attB. HK022 (a lambdoid coliphage with altered att specificity vs lambda) integrates in the torS-torT intergenic region \u2014 NOT leuX. 44 bp window from NC_000913.3 containing the 7 bp common-core overlap AGGTGAA (the solid, source-verified element); the exact minimal BOB\u2032 boundaries are not pinned to a primary figure and are PROVISIONAL. Cognate phage site: HK022_attP.",
      "dcterms:references": [
        {
          "@id": "https://identifiers.org/pubmed:2146253"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://identifiers.org/pubmed:11591683"
