      "cat:claimValue": "{\"application\": \"targeted protein degradation (PROTAC)\", \"bifunctional_molecule\": \"chloroalkane-VHL ligand\", \"effect\": \"ubiquitin-proteasome-mediated degradation of HaloTag7 fusions\"}",
      "cat:confidence": "high",
      "cat:crossChecked": false,
      "cat:sourceQuote": "incorporate small molecule VHL ligands to successfully degrade HaloTag7 fusion proteins... due to their ability to chemically knock down widely used HaloTag7 fusion proteins in a general fashion.",
