      "cat:sourceQuote": "The paper states: \"DNA encoding the SpA sorting signal (residues 474 to 508)\" and identifies the LPETG motif in peptides at positions 470-484 (Table 2, peptide \"KAQALPETGEENPFI\").",
      "cat:sourceQuoteFrom": "primary",
      "cat:sourceSection": "title and abstract",
      "cat:supersedes": {
