      "cat:slug": "Pbla",
      "dcterms:description": "Constitutive sigma-70 promoter (P3) of the beta-lactamase gene (bla / AmpR) from pBR322; 70 bp taken from the minus strand of J01749. Drives bla transcription in the direction opposite the conventional pBR322 numbering. Suboptimal -35/-10 hexamers give weak-to-moderate constitutive strength.",
      "dcterms:references": [
        {
          "@id": "https://identifiers.org/pubmed:358200"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://identifiers.org/pubmed:6178738"
        },
        {
