      "rdfs:label": "SNAP-tag (O6-benzylguanine substrates) is orthogonal to the AGT-derived CLIP-tag (O2-benzylcytosine substrates), so SNAP and CLIP fusions can be labeled simultaneously and specifically with different probes"
    },
