      "cat:slug": "SnoopTag",
      "dcterms:description": "12-aa reactive peptide split from the D4 (CnaA-like) domain of Streptococcus pneumoniae RrgA pilus adhesin (UniProt A7KT94, residues 727\u2013738). Pairs with the protein SnoopCatcher to form a spontaneous, covalent intermolecular isopeptide bond. Orthogonal to the SpyTag/SpyCatcher pair. Sequence verified 100% over 12 aa against GenBank AMD39968.1 (Veggiani 2016 PNAS deposit).",
