      "cat:claimValue": "{\"catalytic_residue\": \"SpyCatcher Glu77 (EQ mutation abolishes reaction)\", \"kinetics\": \"second-order\", \"mechanism\": \"intermolecular isopeptide (amide) bond formation with loss of water\", \"partner\": \"SpyCatcher002 (also backwards-compatible with parental SpyCatcher)\", \"reactive_residue\": \"SpyTag002 Asp (DA mutation abolishes reaction)\", \"reversibility\": \"irreversible (covalent)\"}",
