      "@type": "cat:FunctionalClaim",
      "cat:analysisStatus": "pending",
      "cat:claimType": "induction_kinetics",
      "cat:claimValue": "{\"completion_at_10nM\": \">90% in 15 min\", \"fold_over_SpyTag\": 400, \"fold_over_SpyTag002\": 28, \"half_time_s_at_10uM\": \"<30\", \"interpretation\": \"within the 10^5 to 10^6 M-1 s-1 onset of diffusion-controlled protein-protein interaction\", \"rate_constant_M-1_s-1\": 550000, \"rate_constant_error_M-1_s-1\": 60000, \"reaction\": \"covalent isopeptide bond formation with SpyCatcher003\"}",
      "cat:confidence": "high",
      "cat:crossChecked": false,
      "cat:sourceQuote": "The second-order rate constant for SpyTag003/SpyCatcher003 was 5.5 +/- 0.6 x 10[5] M[-1]s[-1] (mean +/- 1 SD, n = 3), ~400-fold faster than the 1.4 x 10[3] M[-1]s[-1] previously shown for SpyTag/SpyCatcher, and 28-fold faster than the 2.0 x 10[4] M[-1]s[-1] for SpyTag002/SpyCatcher002... SpyTag003/SpyCatcher003 reaction went to >90% completion in 15 min",
      "cat:sourceQuoteFrom": "primary",
