      "cat:slug": "T7_tag",
      "dcterms:description": "T7 tag (gene 10 leader peptide): the N-terminal 11-residue epitope MASMTGGQQMG of bacteriophage T7 Gene product 10A (major capsid protein). Functions both as a translational leader in T7-based expression vectors and as a short immunological epitope tag recognised by anti-T7 monoclonal antibodies. Atomic: the 11 aa are the complete functional unit with no internal sub-features. Distinct from the upstream DNA 5' UTR RBS element (T7_g10_leader).",
      "dcterms:references": [
