        "@id": "part:rrnBT1_claim_factor_enhancement_provenance"
      },
      "rdfs:label": "NusA enhances rrnB T1 termination in vitro to levels matching in-vivo estimates, consistent with the short (4-nt) U-tract being partly rate-limiting in isolation."
    },
