      "rdfs:label": "Thrombin's extended cleavage consensus is P2=Pro (dominant), P1=Arg (obligatory) and a small P1' residue, with P3'=Arg preferred; LVPRGS matches the core P2-Pro/P1-Arg/P1'-small determinants"
